{"type": "article", "id": 21894, "title": "北欧风格的扶手椅", "description": "", "date": "2016-02-04T07:30:13Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 32, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607122301qAHsv2BhTWDLep0d.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">巴黎设计师 samuel accoceberry 带来了一组扶手椅和沙发，都接近北欧的极简风格，用橡木或者胡桃木搭配彩色的垫子。扶手椅 paleta 的名字是一种球拍，扶手的形状与球拍类似。而 concha 在西班牙语中是贝壳的意思，沙发就有像贝壳一样旋转和半包围的形状，明亮的黄色让它具有热情的特征。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071222589YtWkmFVUiM13wqC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.98777506\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"placeholder\"></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122259V6zsk5noePC0y8Tw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.62469438\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122259Kp5yxY4l8sDnSico.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.8594132\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px; height: 305px; width: 375px; left: 518px; top: 1101px;\" class=\"dragged\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122300uiUJfyplaYXrvMSR.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.81418093\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122300e1DAFmu6PkWOxb9l.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.88264059\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p><br></p>\n\n\n"}